ted to whole seconds (DateUtils.toLongDate). When a metadata change\nlanded in the same wall-clock second as a previous fetch, the ETag was\nunchanged, so clients could be served a stale 304 Not Modified.\n\nThis also intermittently broke CI: DataSetMetadataTest.\ndataSetMetadataEtagFunctionalityTest asserts the ETag changes after a\ndataset is created, which collided whenever the create happened in the\nsame second as the prior read (~25-30% of master api-test runs).\n\nSwitch to DateUtils.toLongDateWithMillis so the timestamp keeps\nmillisecond precision. The MD5 hash length is unchanged.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"},"id":"d9f291f591aeb3e2d629267b330757619b15a9ce","tree_id":"f8105f16a0e905cb19b0bafa9c2a8483c72ee91d","timestamp":"2026-05-31T07:16:40Z","committer":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"}